Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:34.26,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my Raiku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:38.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has the powers of both Head \NCaptain Yamamoto’s Ryujinjakka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:42.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Substitute Soul \NReaper’s Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.83,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,As strong as you are, Head Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:51.79,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot remain unscathed after \Nan attack with such power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:01.32,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.01,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,This ends right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:11.68,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:12.82,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.41,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.75,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,This…can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.71,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.03,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! It’s too much for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.63,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,This young lady…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.88,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Is she trying to protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:25.09,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t absorb any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.68,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.16,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.57,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.49,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.45,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.65,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.28,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.32,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.31,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Totally ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.67,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.26,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.04,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you protect a Mod Soul like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:50.60,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get the wrong idea you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.38,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll take more than a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,before I need to be protected by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.60,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:00.52,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,You may be a Mod Soul,\Nbut you’re just a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.93,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Be a bit more honest with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.03,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.34,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:14.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.96,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.88,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.21,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.42,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia! He’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:23.85,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Kageroza?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.54,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.77,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.41,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Kageroza…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.22,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard won’t stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.91,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi, you’re okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.59,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.83,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It won’t do any good, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.73,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t fight with that Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.63,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:48.59,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you try to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nozomi doesn’t \Nwant to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.57,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn’t want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.48,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.48,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.46,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she doesn’t \Nwant to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.73,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi’s creator…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.78,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Nozomi’s father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.12,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,The research is about to be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.56,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You mean taking over \Nthe World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Soul Society?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.09,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn’t make Nozomi happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.94,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Won’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.97,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It would make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.48,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,So Nozomi should be happy, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.81,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spouting nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi’s not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.92,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.24,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.62,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You talk as though you \Nunderstand Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:07.29,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you,\Nno one understands Nozomi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.13,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.63,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.60,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s simple, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.52,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, Nozomi and I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,were born from the Reishi \Nof a single Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.58,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.00,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what it sounded like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:48.23,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.43,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,At least say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.02,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.11,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.41,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you haven’t forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Quit laughing at every little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.33,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.85,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi always knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:27.25,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,If she was captured, \Nwe would become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.45,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,That she would become your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:34.06,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why she tried \Nto keep her distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.63,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to push everyone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.16,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you, Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.30,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,But then, you began to feel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:49.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,an attachment to these people \Nwho tried to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What’s your name? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.47,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you from? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.07,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won’t tell you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.98,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go away! Pervert! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.06,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep your hands off me, pervert! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.83,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not my concern. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don’t worry, Nozomi. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:08.34,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here on, we’ll protect you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.58,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That won’t be necessary. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.27,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’ll fix things so he \Nwon’t have to protect me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.80,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I enter here and close the gateway,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no one will find me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.67,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo and the others, all of \Nus, said we’d protect you! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:26.00,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this what you really want? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:29.08,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lots of good things will happen \Nif you keep on living! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.27,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys are all alike. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.34,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You’re all lousy perverts. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don’t go putting me with him! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At any rate, I don’t know \Nwhy I want to protect you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I heard it…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a voice telling me I \Nhave to protect you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.87,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are an idiot, after all. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.42,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m a burden. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.09,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone tries to protect me… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.26,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don’t have the power \Nto do the same for them. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.01,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I thought of \Nwanting to protect you… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.80,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had a sword. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:17.48,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why she couldn’t \Ntell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You nerdy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.08,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Quit mouthing off like \Nyou know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.95,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t go telling \NNozomi how she feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.57,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Mod Soul…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.67,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi is me, and I am Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:37.17,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Nozomi herself if what \NI am saying is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.19,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.28,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I said not to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.37,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Kageroza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:11.71,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.63,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.67,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on fighting \Nme in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.38,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.14,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s futile in your \Ncurrent condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.96,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.27,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, we’re going back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.22,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,to where we belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.81,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,To how we should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.62,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.77,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.12,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:41.04,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.67,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I’ll take you by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.84,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.78,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:51.09,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:52.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,-You…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.22,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.26,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,-Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:55.81,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.65,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.32,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:04.23,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.36,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Now’s your chance! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.97,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.95,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.17,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you waiting for?! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.61,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.21,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:24.37,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a Mod Soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:27.01,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,but you’re a total failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.69,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll eliminate you \Ncompletely from both
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the World of the Living \Nand the Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.44,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,You pathetic fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.27,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Tenran!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.37,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.05,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.10,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.62,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Genryusai Yamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:24.82,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don’t have \Ntime for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.14,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:08.10,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.24,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:11.38,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, you still have your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:18.87,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.29,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.27,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:49.67,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You…get away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.26,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:55.76,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:59.14,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,But you can make it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.91,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not going without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.87,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.06,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you’re heavy! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.29,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kon…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.67,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.91,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You told me once before…to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.94,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’s my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:29.90,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.57,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.41,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,No! We’re going together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.35,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be okay. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.57,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.14,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.25,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,No! We’re not doing it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I’m getting away together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.31,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,You’re such a stupid pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.69,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shitotsusansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.61,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.68,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.71,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you doing this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.71,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,My Spiritual Pressure’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there for just one more attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:11.50,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi, I have you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.43,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.19,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:34.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Please… Just one is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:39.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.04,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go back…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.48,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,To where we belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.38,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.78,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,I took out a little insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.46,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I slipped near the slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:42.42,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,My Raiku is even capable \Nof replicating myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:48.56,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,The me you defeated was \Nnothing more than a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:54.04,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.05,B2,NOZOMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:12.62,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi… Let’s go back…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.58,B2,KAGEROZA,0000,0000,0000,,to where we belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:22.01,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.63,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:21.29,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:24.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why do that for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always end \Nup getting protected,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:29.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and not able to do anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:33.37,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no point for \Nme to live like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.85,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:37.92,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:40.93,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve completed freezed the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.47,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then let’s go and help \Nrescue Kurosaki and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:44.54,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:47.74,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Zaraki and Madarame’s Spiritual \NPressures have produced a fissure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.38,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll need to deal with that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:51.37,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:53.14,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Now the protective barrier was destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:55.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,due to Miss Nozomi’s technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:56.33,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.60,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,The Head Captain and Kurosaki’s \Ncombined techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,opened a huge hole in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:04.68,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t make it in time.
